1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
Demon Bloodline... activated.

2
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:06,200
Wait... this isn't my dorm.

3
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:09,800
Coarse cloth, mildew, cobwebs... where am I?

4
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:13,400
The face in the mirror... that isn't me.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:22,500
Lin Wan'er — a minister's daughter, made imperial consort,
framed for witchcraft, cast into the cold palace. Three whole years.

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:28,800
My lady! Madam Liu is here —
on the Empress's orders, to send you to your death!

7
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:30,600
Presenting Madam Liu—

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Consort Lin, the Empress is merciful — she grants you a whole corpse.
You ought to be grateful.

9
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:44,500
I can't fight them, begging is useless...
Did I cross over just to die all over again?

10
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,400
Host near death — Demon Bloodline, force-activating.

11
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,400
Your... your eyes?!

12
00:00:53,700 --> 00:01:00,700
Minor demon "Madam Liu" slain. EXP +10.
Demon Bloodline is now Level 1.

13
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:05,800
From this day on, no one decides whether I live or die.

14
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:12,200
Madam Liu... was a demon.
So how many more are hiding in this cold palace?
